title: Cafe Clock
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Western, Moroccan, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Located in the medina of Fes in a nice building. Friendly wait staff. Many choices for vegans. Wi-fi. Atmosphere is a blend of tourists and local Moroccan youth. Special events such as cooking school, concerts, calligraphy classes, and movie night.
